   101→// By default, IREE does not enable the Armv9-A streaming SVE mode in the
   102→// presence of scalable vectors (even when using `+sme`), as currently there's
   103→// no cost model of when it could be beneficial. This flag will effectively make
   104→// IREE/LLVM switch from SVE to SSVE in dispatch regions with supported
   105→// scalable vector operations.
